that's open for 24 hours.

135
00:10:18,684 --> 00:10:19,852
No.

136
00:10:21,087 --> 00:10:23,356
That's not the coffee

137
00:10:23,422 --> 00:10:26,292
I want to drink now.

138
00:10:26,492 --> 00:10:28,027
This is what I want.

139
00:10:28,527 --> 00:10:32,264
With two spoonful of sugar
and one spoonful of coffee.

140
00:10:32,565 --> 00:10:35,034
It has to be made by someone else.

141
00:10:36,235 --> 00:10:39,138
Sitting at a desk wiped by someone else

142
00:10:39,238 --> 00:10:42,041
and wearing shoes
polished by someone else,

143
