186
00:13:51,197 --> 00:13:52,665
Just answer it.

187
00:13:57,002 --> 00:13:59,338
Gal... Gal-hee.

188
00:14:00,906 --> 00:14:02,975
I'm home.

189
00:14:04,777 --> 00:14:05,845
The others?

190
00:14:07,913 --> 00:14:10,983
They all went home.

191
00:14:11,717 --> 00:14:12,551
So you mean

192
00:14:12,618 --> 00:14:15,287
