199
00:14:37,009 --> 00:14:38,344
So I wanted to ask you a favor.

200
00:14:40,145 --> 00:14:42,248
By the way,
why are you stuttering like that?

201
00:14:42,882 --> 00:14:46,118
Are you still in the office?

202
00:14:46,252 --> 00:14:48,554
Gosh, no.

203
00:14:48,621 --> 00:14:51,624
Hey, I'm the one
who can never skip a meal, not the fish.

204
00:14:51,790 --> 00:14:55,327
I'm sure the fish is fine. Don't worry.

205
00:14:56,528 --> 00:14:57,730
